180
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:34,080
[SPEAKER_00] i radosnih.

181
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:36,860
[SPEAKER_00] ono što mene najviše veseli

182
00:13:36,860 --> 00:13:40,139
[SPEAKER_00] je to što sam uvijek osjećala,

