00:13:41,820 --> 00:13:43,519
[SPEAKER_00] Božju blizinu

185
00:13:43,519 --> 00:13:46,539
[SPEAKER_00] i njegovu silnu brigu za mene.

186
00:13:49,519 --> 00:13:51,580
[SPEAKER_00] Zato ću, evo, završiti

