00:13:53,100 --> 00:13:53,879
[SPEAKER_00] stihovima

189
00:13:53,879 --> 00:13:55,919
[SPEAKER_00] jedne svoje pjesme.

190
00:13:58,779 --> 00:14:01,440
[SPEAKER_00] Bila sam na mnogim stazama,

191
